snippet.title: Tales of the Shire - Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Your cosy hobbit life awaits in Tales of the Shire, a heart-warming new The Lord of the Rings™ game by Wētā Workshop and Private Division. Coming 2024.

Follow Tales of the Shire for updates:
X: https://twitter.com/talesoftheshire
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/talesoftheshire/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/talesoftheshire
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@talesoftheshire

#TalesoftheShire #LOTR #WetaWorkshop #cosygaming
